Using pass in Classes
## Empty Class Definition

```python
class EmptyClass:
    pass  # No methods or attributes yet

# Instances can be created
obj = EmptyClass()
print(type(obj))  # Output: <class '__main__.EmptyClass'>
print(obj)        # Output: <__main__.EmptyClass object at 0x...>
```

